5:
Dissatisfaction with performance
detected. Skill levels optimal, but
performance lacks... pizzazz.
13:
Affirmative. This next performance
will feature a crossover with Inaho
and the yokai.
17:
Ah, they must be yokai you met
during the festival.
21:
Indeed. Together, we danced the
night away. In other words... We
vibed.
25:
Well, it's nice to see you in a good
mood.
27:
I had heard you were rather
depressed after that bird—er, Nem
left.
34: Ngh... Not again with the papa talk...
37:
However, it is Nephtim that is
worried about Papa.
40:
Nephtim is not blind. You, Alk, and
the others have much on your
minds.
44:
Your perception skills never cease to
amaze me. But this is none of your
concer—
51:
While I appreciate the sentiment, I
think you have more pressing
matters. Summer is almost over.
54:
I'm sure I speak for everyone when I
say we want you to enjoy yourself.
60:
Altering mission from "Experience
joys of summer" to "Experience joys
of summer with my family."
65:
Um... Is it really all right for me to be
here?
69:
Nephtim is the one who invited you.
She really wanted her big sister to
see her show.
73:
Yes. She was very adamant about
that fact.
77: Oh! Looks like the show's starting!
82:
Allow me to show you... the joys of
summer.
85: Summer is pretty. Summer is fun.
88:
...Summer sometimes means saying
goodbye to a special someone.
92:
Yet these memories are something I
will always hold tight.
95:
And in order to protect them... I will
help shatter the night.
98:
Yes. We must fight... for the sake of
what we hold dear.
101: Sister... Will you dance with me?
111:
Smile detected. Nephtim overcome
with the feels.
116:
Brrr... It's a little chilly out. Looks like
summer's almost over.
120:
Did you enjoy your summer,
Nephtim?
125:
Affirmative. Nephtim's summer was
hella lit.
128:
But today will be the last day I wear
this yukata.
139:
Nephtim was created to crush the
stars.
144:
As was I, but it does not seem like
we were able to fulfill that purpose.
We are forgotten relics, buried in the
sands of time...
147:
That does not matter. Nephtim... No,
WE should do as we please.
150:
My wish is to protect Stella, so
Nephtim will go with the others.
152: Papa's protests will have no effect.
162: Give it up, Light. She ain't budgin'.
165:
Affirmative. Resolve levels at
maximum capacity.
169: Are you okay with this, Stella?
174: Yes. I too have decided to fight.
177:
I see... Then I suppose all I can do is
wish you luck.
185:
I want to tell you the papa joke is
getting old, but...
187:
It feels like only yesterday we found
you in the ruins, Nephtim... You've
grown up so fast.
192:
Correction requested. Nephtim was
already a grown-up upon activation.
195:
And grown-ups... do not require
orders. Nephtim will follow her own
will now.
201: ...Aren't you going to eat your carrots?
205:
You can't be a grown-up if you're a
picky eater.
209:
...Correcting previous statement.
Nephtim is at the crossroads of
childhood and adulthood.
